{"tid":285600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國三大滅門奇案之首 福建滅門案","createTime":"2017-06-16T03:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T04:05:30.000Z","uid":4304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6db60ce1c74e1498735c41b027635364fae6af0b","tid":285600,"uid":4304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:16:17.000Z","msg":"最近有d巴打都出post講奇案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而本人一直都對d奇案幾有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而最近見到台灣上左套「神秘家族」<br />\n電影由真實改編，所以上網睇左依單案既資料<br />\n最後疑犯講個句其實都幾心寒<br />\n大家可以討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下文章都係上網搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前世今生輪迴強姦滅門奇案<br />\n最詭異令人髮指的當屬&ldquo;福建一家四口滅門案&rdquo;,該案被專家稱為&ldquo;中國3大滅門奇案之首&rdquo;。 2014年9月24日警方抓獲涉嫌故意殺人的犯罪嫌疑人李某，成功破獲發生在轄區安溪縣龍涓鄉的一起一家四口被殺案。<br />\n事情的經過是這樣的，李某26歲，3年前就強暴過被害人的妻子，因犯強姦罪被判刑2年6個月，剛刑滿釋放7天再次作案，要知道在中國，刑滿釋放後再作案是極少的，那監獄不把你教育的服服帖帖的能讓你出來嗎？還會經過一系列的心理鑑定、犯罪傾向評估等。然而李某福出來後把某忠一家都殺了，用的是殺豬刀，男主人死在屋內被連捅7刀，再用被子蓋住，其妻子與兩個孩子一併殺害後，扭曲得塞在裝稻穀的櫃子裡。兩個孩子分別只有12歲和6歲。要說李某與被害人一家有何深仇大恨也還說的過去，問題是完全沒有，三年前的強暴據說李某是在公交站遇到被害人妻子，完全不認識，一路尾隨2個小時，在樹林裡將其打得半死並強暴。據傳被捕時李某深吸了一口煙說&ldquo;天道好輪迴，這一世你們已經不認識我了，但我還記得是誰讓我家破人亡，上一世是我了結你們，下一世我還會來找你們的！&rdquo;就這樣，一家四口，與兇手毫不相識的一家四口被這樣的理由殺死。警方鑑定李某並沒有精神問題。你會相信輪迴的說法嗎？<br />\n<br />\n另外上網見到有人改左個漫畫<br />\n不過殘體字，但睇完都覺得好變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/111343_d23ea364b67b04c60f6a99ecfee8a74a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F111343_d23ea364b67b04c60f6a99ecfee8a74a.jpg&h=27c4472d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/111344_e2d4f54c458a3d002e3855280aab2c87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F111344_e2d4f54c458a3d002e3855280aab2c87.jpg&h=2a712cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/111345_a75a83c709b333aff01a52f682244eb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F111345_a75a83c709b333aff01a52f682244eb9.jpg&h=23303253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20140925/52941636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20140925%2F52941636&d=e%2BxDHBxlilpaJVkZfg9g4EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=17290396\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20140925%2F52941636&h=2678dac6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20140925/52941636</a>"},{"pid":"fa9b6798a33f61d87e522aff284c3c7350bb29b9","tid":285600,"uid":4304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"D圖放出黎咁細張既<br />\n<br />\n大家可以click入條link都睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.douban.com/group/topic/98673963/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.douban.com%2Fgroup%2Ftopic%2F98673963%2F&d=e%2BxDHBxlilpaJVkZfg9g4EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=74cce35f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.douban.com/group/topic/98673963/</a>"},{"pid":"36ddffe2f1f9e9d069ab942979b99e921ce11fe0","tid":285600,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:24:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D圖放出黎咁細張既<br />\n<br />\n大家可以click入條link都睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.douban.com/group/topic/98673963/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.douban.com%2Fgroup%2Ftopic%2F98673963%2F&d=e%2BxDHBxlilpaJVkZfg9g4EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=74cce35f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.douban.com/group/topic/98673963/</a></blockquote><br />\n漫畫名三生三世十里紅花"},{"pid":"720974594c0f849af558e22653844057816ac8cf","tid":285600,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/19fe000192e414671df6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F19fe000192e414671df6&h=c1ce64b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俊? 邊撚到俊呀睇過"},{"pid":"f2a68e0dac2baae676366bccfc03ad7c9488eeac","tid":285600,"uid":4304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/19fe000192e414671df6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F19fe000192e414671df6&h=c1ce64b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俊? 邊撚到俊呀睇過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n典型蝗樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8af59c174b34923a1de1528f14aa5bac87b91f","tid":285600,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34af0f3d9097f120ffcba77160710867da59612f","tid":285600,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:02:39.000Z","msg":"支那人係咪唔撚知咩叫奇案?"},{"pid":"ff2091cedb9b321a3bce213dd343eba9d2fbb000","tid":285600,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:05:30.000Z","msg":"發生係大陸 好出奇咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}